  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Kato Clan <br />Your wisdom, modesty, and unshaking ideals have led you this far in life, and nothing short of death will stop your dreams. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score by 1, to a max of 20.</li><li>You gain proficiency in Persuasion and you may use Wisdom instead of Charisma for checks made with this skill.</li><li>After every Long Rest, you gain a Will of Fire.</li><li>When you fall to 0 hit points while in combat, the closest ally within 60 feet of you that can see you gains a Will of Fire.</li></ul>",
